{
  "stem": "15028.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They had them-- they had a church.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had the three shuls, and the gentiles had a big-- a big church.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And somehow, there was a certain respect for the-- each other, remain, until it came, Christmas Evening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Christmas night, I was told-- remember, I was a kid-- that they went into church.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the-- and the Pope-- not the Pope, the priest told them that a Jew told them the story about Christmas, and that the Jews killed Jesus.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And by going out, about 12:00 at night, the youngsters-- not the older, my father's age and so on-- the young, 18 and 20, when they walked out from the church, 12:00 at night, and-- they threw stones in Jewish houses, threw stones in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that happened that night, that usually at Christmas night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then it was quiet and continued-- life was continued.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say every year, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the gentiles didn't do much about it, didn't make a big fuss.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a common.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the story was going, when the-- when the priest told them that the Jews had killed Jesus, then they walked to the door, like make-believe.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We'll go out and kill the Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, they killed Jesus.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then he yelled out, children, children, hold it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Hold it, hold it!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Come back.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now mind, we were told.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father, the friends told them of what's going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they-- hold back, come back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is not the Jews, what killed Jesus.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's many, many hundreds years ago, thousands of years ago.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this is-- this is good Jews, and they didn't kill Jesus.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they called them back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The injunction was, already, given to the young people when they threw the stones.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
